'''Southern Campus''' was a school of higher education on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. It was one of the dozen satellite campuses of the [[University of Coruscant/Legends|University of Coruscant]].

In [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]], one week before the scheduled vote of the [[Military Creation Act/Legends|Military Creation Act]], 7,000 students of the Southern Campus camped outside the [[Senate Building/Legends|Senate Building]], protesting against the Act.

